      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Matlacha%2C_Florida"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "Matlacha is an Old Florida fishing village known for its brightly colored art galleries, island boutiques, seafood restaurants, and traditional Floridian cottages.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        4
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Matlacha%2C_Florida"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "WildChild Art Gallery, opened in 2000, showcases contemporary art in a historic fishing cottage at Matlacha's heart.",
